<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Signs_and_symptoms">Signs and symptoms</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Ulcerative_colitis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Signs and symptoms">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<table class="wikitable" style="float:right; margin-left:6px;">
<caption>Signs and symptoms</caption>
<tr>
<th></th>
<th>Crohn's disease</th>
<th>Ulcerative colitis</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Defecation</td>
<td>Often <a href="/wiki/Porridge" title="Porridge">porridge</a>-like<sup id="cite_ref-internetmedicin_3-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-internetmedicin-3"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup>,<br />
sometimes <a href="/wiki/Steatorrhea" title="Steatorrhea">steatorrhea</a></td>
<td>Often mucus-like<br />
and with blood<sup id="cite_ref-internetmedicin_3-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-internetmedicin-3"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/Rectal_tenesmus" title="Rectal tenesmus">Tenesmus</a></td>
<td>Less common<sup id="cite_ref-internetmedicin_3-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-internetmedicin-3"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
<td>More common<sup id="cite_ref-internetmedicin_3-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-internetmedicin-3"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/Fever" title="Fever">Fever</a></td>
<td>Common<sup id="cite_ref-internetmedicin_3-4" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-internetmedicin-3"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
<td>Indicates severe disease<sup id="cite_ref-internetmedicin_3-5" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-internetmedicin-3"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/Fistula" title="Fistula">Fistulae</a></td>
